Our Reporter Comedian and actor Ayo Makun, who is popularly known as AY, has struck a deal with one of the housing properties company in Nigeria; Revolution Plus Property. As revealed by AY, the company will for the next five years sponsor his annual show AY Live. Sharing the news on his social handle with a video where he is seen signing the contract at the company office in Lagos, he wrote: “What a good way to start the year. Thanks to @revolutionplusproperty for the 5 years sponsorship deal for AY Live.”  Captioning the video, AY wrote, “5years partnership deal as official sponsor for AY Live.” In line with the new contract, the comedian also said they will be giving out a house in Lekki, Lagos on Easter Sunday, which happens to be his show date.